    "body": "@akashnimare thank you for the prompt reply. Please with regard to \n\n```\nmainWindow = new BrowserWindow({\n        width: 1024,\n        height: 680,\n    });\n```\n\nWouldn't running this on code initiate new instance of browser windows ? My authentication depend on the localstorage data from the localStorage . How to i utilise those data when user exit and reopen the app ?\n"
