    "body": "@nuruddeensalihu The `localStorage` session is persisted even when calling `new BrowserWindow()`.  \n\nRead more about `webContents` sessions here http://electron.atom.io/docs/api/session/\n\nYou can demonstrate this by opening the default app and running `localStorage.setItem('foo', 'bar')` then closing and reopening and running `localStorage.getItem('foo')`\n\nYou will see that the value has been persisted\n"
  },
